Italian retail sales rose 2 . 5 pct in July yr / yr . Retail sales of medium and large firms in Italy rose 2 . 5 percent year - on - year in July , national statistics institute ISTAT said on Monday . It said the retail sales index ( 1990 = 100 ) was 134 . 5 in July against 131 . 2 in the same 1995 month . Retail sales in the first seven months of 1996 rose 5 . 8 percent compared to the same period last year - - Rome newsroom + 396 678 - 2505 
